<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="evacuate-v">evacuate <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪ'vækjueɪt/    美 /ɪ'vækjueɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>疏散；撤出</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Children were evacuated from London to escape the bombing.
为躲避轰炸，孩子们都撤离了伦敦。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>During the war he was evacuated to Scotland.
战争期间他被撤离到苏格兰。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>撤离</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Employees were urged to evacuate their offices immediately.
已敦促各雇员立即从办公室撤出。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Locals were told to evacuate.
当地居民已收到撤离的通知。</p></div></div>